&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help design and implement next-level testing infrastructure and tooling for our Globality platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on test infrastructure issues related to engineering stakeholders you engage with, and the entire Globality product stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop working knowledge of the entire Globality application stack including tests at all levels and purposes. (Levels: Unit, Integration, and End-to-end; Purposes: Functional, Scale/Load, Performance)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, share, and nurture the adoption of best practices in code health, testing, testability, and maintainability in collaboration with the wider Engineering organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze complex software systems and collaborate with others to improve the overall design, testability, and quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strive for the fastest feedback possible. Test parallelization should be a top priority. You see distributed systems as a core challenge of good test automation infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and communicate test results in a timely, effective, and automated manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Above all else: Protect the health of the Production environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience building and maintaining complex software systems using production-grade engineering practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience developing, implementing, and supporting test automation frameworks and tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of containerization and orchestration technologies such as Docker and Kubernetes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing, implementing, and optimizing CI/CD pipelines to enable reliable, efficient, and rapid software delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong collaboration skills, with the ability to work effectively in distributed teams and communicate asynchronously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with testing frameworks and tools such as JUnit, Pytest, Cucumber (BDD), and Cypress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with build and dependency management tools such as Maven and Gradle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with CI/CD platforms such as Jenkins, CircleCI, and Drone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing and testing APIs using REST, GraphQL, and/or gRPC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in integration and performance testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of modern software quality, automation, and release engineering best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
