&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with business users, translating technical issues into clear explanations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer and support cloud-based platforms and services (Office 365, Azure, AWS, Active Directory, Slack, Okta)&lt;/li&gt;
