&lt;li&gt;Identify and resolve frontend performance bottlenecks in data-intensive views&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in sprint planning, technical discussions, and architecture conversations alongside senior engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
