&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building enterprise B2B products with complex data models or multi-step workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to AI/ML-powered product features (streaming responses, model outputs in UI, confidence indicators)&lt;/li&gt;
